    <h1>Marketing Qualified Lead (MQL)</h1>
    <p class="description">A prospect who has demonstrated sufficient interest and ICP fit to warrant sales attention — determined by a lead scoring model jointly defined by marketing and sales.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
