            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes, but it's operationally painful at scale. For companies with fewer than 50 leads per month, manual qualification in a shared CRM spreadsheet works. Above that volume, lead scoring and routing logic becomes impossible to maintain without marketing automation software.</p></div></div>
